{"tid":2240871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邀請愛國的政府官員和藍絲上北京，一齊試武漢肺炎疫苗","createTime":"2020-10-13T03:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T11:50:14.000Z","uid":108201,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4525e83842518c4db2c0473b896177f6e16acd2","tid":2240871,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"愛國的政府官員和藍絲，仲唔上去北京打針做實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？特別係特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國藥集團武肺疫苗已經<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">在北京和武漢開放預約接種</span></strong></span>，目前已有逾7萬人進行了接種報名。據瞭解，雖然所有人羣都可以進行預約，但是公司會優先選擇出國留學生，特別是今年11月至明年1月需出國的留學生進行接種。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302ce3bfacbfa3c58c6c3bd1927c57c8d284ed75","tid":2240871,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"為黨國犧牲係光榮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/121109165_1581364028722326_6325417112630502914_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=bTT6II7a1dYAX-BnUwg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=985cbbbc83cefd5b2e9425947af1c7bb&amp;oe=5FAB430B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F121109165_1581364028722326_6325417112630502914_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DbTT6II7a1dYAX-BnUwg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D985cbbbc83cefd5b2e9425947af1c7bb%26oe%3D5FAB430B&h=7ce67223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I-G-ojVMiZ9jHekVWByhKT-rh7I=/1587x1000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F4Z5SZR3V5FHPJPTZG6E335ZBI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fr